text: KPRC-FM (100.7 FM) is a radio station broadcasting a Spanish adult hits format. Licensed to Salinas, California, United States, it serves the Santa Cruz area. The station is currently owned by iHeartMedia, Inc.. Its studios are in Salinas, and the transmitter is on Mount Toro, 10 miles south. ==External links== * * * PRC-FM Category:Radio stations established in 1993 PRC-FM Category:1993 establishments in California Category:IHeartMedia radio stations
